{
  "stem": "4570.2",
  "chunk_idx": 13,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 9.4,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And she also wanted to find her Czech guy.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "And she was standing near a woman with two little children.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "And the woman had one child up, and the second was running around, and the woman was struggling.",
      "word_count": 18
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "And Helen picked up the child and held the child.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 21,
      "text": "I was very aware of it.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 22,
      "text": "I can't say why.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 23,
      "text": "Anyhow, when my turn came to, to come to that guy with the polished boots, and black gloves, and SSS, and he said, left right, left right, I only know that I was on the other side than my Dutch girlfriend that was still holding the child.",
      "word_count": 47
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 24,
      "text": "And somehow, I had the feeling that looking at us that were the one in my group, I had the feeling that I'm in the right group, because they were young.",
      "word_count": 31
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 25,
      "text": "They were looking healthy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 26,
      "text": "And on the other one, there were some older people and children.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 27,
      "text": "And I had a feeling that, that she, she did something awful picking up that child.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 28,
      "text": "She was killed the same day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 45,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 29,
      "text": "[PAUSES FOR 7 SECONDS]",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 46,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "About what?",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 47,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Registration?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Oh, when we went into Auschwitz.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Well, once we-- once we went past Mengele and, and, you know, again, five, five, five, we walk, walk, walk.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "And then, of course, we came to the shower room.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "And by that time, of course, all our luggage was left in the train.",
      "word_count": 14
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I already had the feeling I'll never see my things again.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 48,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then we were again hoarded into some big hall and told to, to watch out that we leave every-- all our clothes together, that we will find it easily.",
      "word_count": 30
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 49,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And when I-- when I undressed, I had a little photo of Goldie and a silver Buddha.",
      "word_count": 17
    }
  ],
